review_title: GPS NOT WORKING PROPERLY HARD TO UNDERSTAND MANUAL NO SUPPORT
review:
IT IS A TERRIBLE PRODUCT WORTH NO MORE THAN $20. THE USER MANUAL IS TERRIBLE. MY UNIT BEEPED EVERY 30 SECONDS FOR NO REASON. IT ONLY STOPPED WHEN YOU ARRIVED AT YOUR DESTINATION. CLOCK ONLY SHOWS THE CORRECT TIME ON THE INTERFACE. ONCE YOU WERE MOBILE IT HAS THE WRONG TIME. THERE IS NO SUPPORT ON THEIR WEBSITE. MUST USE FACEBOOK. I WAS TOLD THAT WHEN YOU WANTED TO UPDATE THE RECENT MAP, TO REMOVE TE OLD OLD THEN INSTALL THE NEW ONE. WELL IT DOES NOT WORK BECAUSE THE NEW FILE IS TOO BIG. NOW I DO NOT HAVE A MAP FOR MY UNIT. THE MAIN ICON WHEN YOU START THE GPS HAS DISAPPEARED GONE. IT GOES DIRECTLY TO THE NAVIGATION SCREEN. I HAVE LOST THE SETTING ICON AND OTHER FEATURES.
I DO NOT RECOMMEND THIS UNIT TO ANYONE.
author: Snofrog
